name: Imaginary world
description:
Have you ever wanted to escape from this cruel world? 
...
Flee from the harsh reality and the people whose words pierce their feelings. 
...
For me, Books are that world. A new land that sincerely heals and fulfill our dreams. Even the sorrow that arises in that fantasy world is gentle and embraces us, teaches us, guides us, and lifts us up on our own feet again and again.

-------------

This piece was created as a gift to the 25 contributors who purchased all of my first collection on the Tezos chain. 

Thank you to let me has the opportunity to continue creating works.

This image has only 26 editions. And it has sound.
